<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.2.9">
<l>mēvit toḻutuymmi ṉīrkaḷ vētap puṉita virukkai</l>
<l>nāviṟkoṇ ṭaccutaṉ ṟaṉṉai ñāṉa vitipiḻai yāmē</l>
<l>pūvil pukaiyum viḷakkuñ cāntamu nīru malintu</l>
<l>mēvit toḻumaṭi yārum pakavaru mikka tulakē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Join, worship [and] be saved, you. We won’t fail Acyuta</l>
<l>for the rule of knowledge, taking [our] tongues as the pure seat of the Veda.</l>
<l>The world has increased in divine beings and servants who join [and] worship,</l>
<l>abounding in flowers , incense, lamps, sandal paste and water.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
